_sText:
Decided to make something relatively realistic for a change.

Initially I went way overboard with details and geometry which resulted in major performance issues, so I had to simplify and redesign quite a bit. I need to learn to use 3DSMax so I can use custom models instead of func_details. =/

V1.1

1. Fixed weapon ammo capacity.
2. Replaced carpet brushes with overlays.
3. Fixed player clips.
4. Replaced func_detail with func_brush for ivy's
